  "summary": "omec-project amf Vulnerable to Improper Restriction of Operations within the Bounds of a Memory Buffer",
  "details": "A vulnerability was found in omec-project amf up to 2.1.1. This vulnerability affects unknown code of the component NGReset Message Handler. Performing a manipulation results in memory corruption. The attack is possible to be carried out remotely. The exploit has been made public and could be used. It is recommended to apply a patch to fix this issue.",
